@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
participant "laptop-service" as LaptopService
database "PostgreSQL Laptop DB" as LaptopDB

Customer -> Gateway: GET /api/customers/laptops/
Gateway -> CustomerService: GET /customers/laptops/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> LaptopService: GET /laptops/
LaptopService -> LaptopDB: Query laptops
LaptopDB --> LaptopService: Laptop list
LaptopService --> CustomerService: Laptop list
CustomerService --> Gateway: Response JSON
Gateway --> Customer: Laptop list
@enduml
